sentences: Lucas MacFadden (born October 4, 1972), better known as Cut Chemist, is an American DJ and record producer.
Cut Chemist graduated from University of California, Los Angeles in 1997.
He left Jurassic 5 in 2004.
In a 2006 interview with Billboard, he stated that he had left the group in order to get his solo album finished.
His first solo studio album, The Audience's Listening, was released on July 11, 2006.
In 2015, it was listed by Vice as the 49th greatest dance album of all time.
In 2010, he released a DJ mix, Sound of the Police.
His second solo studio album, Die Cut, was released on March 2, 2018.
